sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard
    participant DSP as DS Pipelines<br/>API Server
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows<br/>Controller
    participant StepPod as Pipeline Step Pods
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry
    participant KServe as KServe Controller
    participant S3 as S3 / MinIO

    Note over User,S3: Workflow 2: ML Pipeline Execution

    User->>Dashboard: Submit pipeline run<br/>(pipeline YAML with DAG)
    Dashboard->>DSP: Pipeline submission via<br/>Fastify BFF sidecar

    DSP->>DSP: Validate pipeline,<br/>create run record in DB
    DSP->>Argo: Compile KFP IR to<br/>Argo Workflow CR

    Argo->>StepPod: Schedule workflow step 1<br/>(with argoexec sidecar)
    StepPod->>S3: Fetch training data<br/>(HTTPS/443)
    StepPod->>StepPod: Execute preprocessing
    StepPod->>S3: Store intermediate artifacts
    StepPod->>MLMD: Record execution metadata<br/>(gRPC)

    Argo->>StepPod: Schedule step 2 (training)
    StepPod->>S3: Load preprocessed data
    StepPod->>StepPod: Train model
    StepPod->>S3: Upload model artifacts<br/>(model.pkl / model weights)
    StepPod->>MLMD: Record artifact lineage<br/>(gRPC)

    Argo->>StepPod: Schedule step 3 (evaluation)
    StepPod->>S3: Load model + test data
    StepPod->>StepPod: Evaluate model metrics
    StepPod->>MLMD: Record evaluation results

    MLMD->>ModelReg: Store model version metadata<br/>and artifact locations (gRPC)
    ModelReg->>S3: Store artifact reference

    Note over ModelReg,KServe: Optional: auto-deploy to serving
    ModelReg->>KServe: Create InferenceService CR<br/>with model location
    KServe->>S3: Pull model for serving

