sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard
    participant TrustyOp as trustyai-service-operator
    participant EvalJob as Evaluation Job<br/>(lm-eval-harness / Ragas)
    participant MLflow as MLflow Tracking
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service
    participant Guardrails as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant Detectors as Guardrails Detectors<br/>(HAP, PII, regex)
    participant VLLMOrch as vllm-orchestrator-gateway
    participant ModelEndpoint as Model Endpoint<br/>(vLLM)
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant Client as External Client

    Note over User,Client: Workflow 4: Model Evaluation and Guardrails

    %% Evaluation phase
    User->>Dashboard: Configure evaluation job<br/>(select model, framework, metrics)
    Dashboard->>TrustyOp: Create evaluation Job CR

    TrustyOp->>EvalJob: Create K8s Job with<br/>lm-evaluation-harness container
    EvalJob->>ModelEndpoint: Run benchmarks against<br/>model endpoint (OpenAI API)
    ModelEndpoint-->>EvalJob: Inference results
    EvalJob->>MLflow: Record evaluation results<br/>(experiment tracking, HTTP/5000)

    %% Monitoring phase
    TrustyAI->>ModelEndpoint: Monitor deployed model<br/>for bias drift (HTTP)
    TrustyAI->>Prometheus: Push fairness metrics<br/>(HTTP)
    Prometheus-->>Dashboard: Query metrics for display

    %% Guardrails inference path
    Client->>Guardrails: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(HTTPS, OpenAI-compatible)
    Guardrails->>Detectors: Route through detector pipeline
    Note over Detectors: PII detection, content safety,<br/>jailbreak detection
    Detectors-->>Guardrails: Detection results
    Guardrails->>ModelEndpoint: Forward clean request<br/>(OpenAI API)
    ModelEndpoint-->>Guardrails: Model response
    Guardrails->>Detectors: Scan output
    Detectors-->>Guardrails: Output safety results
    Guardrails-->>Client: Filtered response (HTTPS)

    %% Alternative: vllm-orchestrator-gateway path
    Note over VLLMOrch,ModelEndpoint: Alternative: Rust-based content filtering
    Client->>VLLMOrch: POST /v1/chat/completions
    VLLMOrch->>Detectors: Content filtering pipeline
    Detectors-->>VLLMOrch: Filter results
    VLLMOrch->>ModelEndpoint: Forward request
    ModelEndpoint-->>VLLMOrch: Response
    VLLMOrch-->>Client: Filtered response
